    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many useful items in the Pink Summer set that will improve your game. This set will allow you to enjoy the possibilities that the store offers. You will have a large amount of supplies at your disposal, as well as a timeless costume!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that all items in the Pink Summer set cannot be stored in a warehouse, nor can they be transferred to another player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember that you can only buy the starter kit once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The package includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/045cbcf0e95733e4b6e6d37dcec2cad3.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Small Pink Bathing Suit (top, eternal) (1 piece) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/f5b0ddda2fc215582eab55643d7542dd.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Small Pink Bathing Suit (bottom, eternal) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/394bb307bc10a7fcb06c94e2b1367632.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Small Pink Bathing Suit (boots, eternal) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/989318619967028fe35fd421b0dbd104.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Small Pink Bathing Suit (gloves, eternal) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/4adc4795184193342885658904f0e5ff.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Wings of Rest (30 days) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/1b6f2e747e0e8d503a7c51ae31ded86e.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Lucky Ruby Pickaxe (3 hours) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/0a238adc4018d5180bb0719e3f6560a5.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Armor Protection (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/42c7368225f8ba4fcdcafa60b54404ba.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span>Weapon Protection (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/c03c8e8585a687917d41f39be36f9431.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span> The Great Potion of Experience (3 hours) (1 piece)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174210/extras/0cb3db8b5beb221f105f89061a758618.webp?t=1727166800\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Platinum Experience Potion (1 hour) (10 pcs)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can get the purchased set in the &quot;Gifts&quot; menu of the in-game store.</p>",
